<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Wednesday</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
Stayed at rest in the main city here. Not many people live here, and thsoe who do know very little about the past. People say it was a people called &quot;Akarians&quot; who destoyed this land and all people in it. By what? They don't know. Sounds to me as if it was a nuclear bomb or something. Erundil, my assistant says he found some kind of radiation that could be harmful. <br>
As we elves are immortal we wont be harmed of it, although my ahir gets a bit grey... I could always go to my hair stylist tomorrow. People hear are plae in tehir faces and have greay hair. It looks somewhat hopeless. Actually people heer are quite modern so they make their hed blue like they did in Jasonia, but grey skin and grey hair is sort of their style, such as people in Babkha are brown, elves are tall etc...<br>
I decided for teh safety of my human crew, I'd let them travel home. Many of them got ill when we came here. Theyre immune system, says teh doc, is not eyt attapted to the radiation. So only elves stay here.<br>
Big day tomorow, we're gonna go visit some villages in teh dessert. great I took my Babkhan turban with me.<br>
